  'tos.title':'Terms of Service','tos.meta':'Last updated: May 29, 2026 / Operator: StratAIX',
  'pp.content':'<p>StratAIX (\u201cwe\u201d) sets out how it handles user information in Echo Photo Album (\u201cthe app\u201d) as follows.</p>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">1. Information We Handle</h3><p>The app handles the following information created or selected by the user. All of it is stored <strong class="font-normal text-stone-800">only on the user\u2019s device</strong>.</p><ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 list-none"><li>\u2014 Photos: images selected from the photo library</li><li>\u2014 Audio: recordings made with the microphone</li><li>\u2014 Text: titles, notes and tags</li></ul></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">2. Storage Location & Transmission</h3><p>The app does not send user data to our servers or any third party. It performs no automatic upload to the cloud. Sharing data (exporting a video, sending to other apps) happens solely through the user\u2019s own actions.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">3. Removal of Location (GPS) Data</h3><p>Location data contained in photos (EXIF metadata) is automatically removed when imported into the app.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">4. Automatic Collection & Analytics</h3><p>The app does not automatically collect personally identifiable information. No advertising SDKs or analytics tools are embedded.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">5. In-App Purchase</h3><p>The app uses the App Store / Google Play billing system for the one-time premium unlock (\u00a5500). Payment information is processed by each platform; we do not retain it. Each company\u2019s privacy policy (<a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/en-ww/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-clay">Apple</a> / <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-clay">Google</a>) applies.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">6. Permissions</h3><ul class="space-y-1.5 list-none"><li>\u2014 Microphone: recording audio</li><li>\u2014 Photos (read): selecting photos</li><li>\u2014 Photos (add): saving exported videos</li></ul><p class="mt-3">Permissions are requested only when the relevant feature is used. If denied, that feature is limited but other features remain available.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">7. Children\u2019s Privacy</h3><p>The app is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect children\u2019s information.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">8. Changes to This Policy</h3><p>If we change this policy, we will notify you by posting on this page.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">9. Contact</h3><p>For questions about this policy, contact <a href="mailto:support@strataix.net" class="underline hover:text-clay">support@strataix.net</a>.</p></div>',
  'tos.content':'<div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 1 (Application)</h3><p>These Terms of Service (\u201cthese Terms\u201d) define the conditions for using Echo Photo Album (\u201cthe app\u201d) provided by StratAIX (\u201cwe\u201d). Users use the app upon agreeing to these Terms and the <a href="#privacy" class="underline hover:text-clay">Privacy Policy</a>.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 2 (Fees & In-App Purchase)</h3><ul class="space-y-1.5 list-none"><li>\u2014 The app can be downloaded free and used free for the first 3 days or up to 10 saved memories.</li><li>\u2014 Removing the save limit and additional themes (Journal / Gallery) are available via the one-time premium unlock (\u00a5500).</li><li>\u2014 Billing is processed via App Store / Google Play in-app purchase. Refunds follow each platform\u2019s policy.</li></ul></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 3 (Data Management)</h3><p>All app data is stored on the user\u2019s device. If data is lost due to deleting the app, loss or failure of the device, etc., we bear no responsibility for recovery. We recommend periodically saving important data externally, such as by exporting video.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 4 (Prohibited Acts)</h3><ul class="space-y-1.5 list-none"><li>\u2014 Reverse engineering, modifying or redistributing the app</li><li>\u2014 Use for purposes against laws or public order and morals</li><li>\u2014 Acts that infringe the rights of us or third parties</li></ul></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 5 (Intellectual Property)</h3><p>Copyright and other intellectual property rights in the app belong to us or rightful holders. Rights to content created by the user in the app (photos, audio, video) belong to the user.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 6 (Disclaimer)</h3><ul class="space-y-1.5 list-none"><li>\u2014 Except in cases of our willful misconduct or gross negligence, we are not liable for damages arising from use of the app.</li><li>\u2014 The app may not function properly due to OS/device specification changes, force majeure, etc.</li></ul></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 7 (Changes to Terms)</h3><p>We may change these Terms. The revised Terms take effect upon posting on this page. Continued use after the change is deemed acceptance of the revised Terms.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 8 (Governing Law & Jurisdiction)</h3><p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Japan. The Tokyo District Court shall be the exclusive court of first instance for disputes regarding the app.</p></div>\n      <div><h3 class="text-stone-900 font-normal mb-2">Article 9 (Contact)</h3><p>For questions about these Terms, contact <a href="mailto:support@strataix.net" class="underline hover:text-clay">support@strataix.net</a>.</p></div>',
